I don't see any reason to think a mod is causing this. I'd delete and reinstall "Serenity" which is the most recent DLC, Breaking Ground.

Go into C:\GOG Games\Kerbal Space Program\GameData\SquadExpansion and just wipe out the entire "Serenity" folder. Back it up if you're worried.

Then do whatever GOG requires you to do to install the DLC again.
